articles.title: Stock Market Today: Dow, S&P Live Updates for November 10 - Bloomberg
articles.description: European equities fell, tracking a global retreat after Federal Reserve Chair Jerome Powell warned interest rates may have to climb further. The pound swung between gains and losses as UK data showed the economy stagnating.
